 Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nOrbis 🌐 — Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776117671474,"responseId":"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f","__openclaw":{"id":"faf39631","seq":7}}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776206767604}}
